00:24:09,578 --> 00:24:11,058
- Boy, I hope not.

556
00:24:11,101 --> 00:24:13,539
You want me to ask the nurses
to swap your linens out?

557
00:24:13,582 --> 00:24:15,541
- Yes, please.
