If it's not
the right choice for you--

704
00:30:29,175 --> 00:30:30,741
- I can't ask
for the money back now.

705
00:30:30,785 --> 00:30:32,743
I'm in a no-win situation here.

706
00:30:34,963 --> 00:30:37,879
