00:32:37,216 --> 00:32:38,347
- Well, why don't I
walk you out?

745
00:32:38,391 --> 00:32:40,436
- Oh, thank you.

746
00:32:40,480 --> 00:32:43,004
- Oh, hey, there you are.

747
00:32:43,048 --> 00:32:44,223
Good news.

748
00:32:44,266 --> 00:32:45,572
I don't know how you
managed to get Abby

